<title>rạḥty̱ yạ rb ḥqạaⁿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- rạḥty yạ rb ḥqạaⁿ ạ̉n ly fyk mkạn wạtẖq lạ ạ̉nsy̱ mnk mhmạ ḍạq by ạlzmạn
 ạlqrạr- (yạ msyḥy yạ ḥyạty yạ sẖfyʿy kl ận klmạ kẖạrt qwạy mnk ʿwny wạlạ̉mạn) 2
 2- tẖạbt qlby yạ rby tẖạbt yạ ṣkẖrty rạfʿ ʿyny ạ̹lyk mnk tạ̉ty qwty
 3- qwẗ fy ạlḍʿf fạḍt mnk yạ rby ạlḥbyb yạ rjạỷy ạ̉nt tsẖfy ḥynmạ ạlqlb ykẖyb</lyrics>
</song>